 supplying natural rubber to domestic and international manufacturers and export processing zones in the field of manufacturing tires, sports shoes, gloves, medical equipment, etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"561\" src=\"/2020_caosuphurieng/datafiles/images/img/2.jpg\" width=\"1000\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>VRG is now an official member of:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Vietnam Chamber of Commerce and Industry (VCCI) since 2003.</li>\r\n	<li>Vietnam Rubber Association (VRA) since 2005.</li>\r\n	<li>Young Entrepreneurs Association (YBA) in Ho Chi Minh City since 2005.</li>\r\n	<li>Ho Chi Minh City Export Business Club (VEXA) since 2010.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>With a staff of experienced and in-depth knowledge in import-export trading business, highly qualified, always learning, updating and improving skills, knowledge, VRG has increasingly met. It is highly required by the market as well as domestic and international customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"630\" src=\"/2020_caosuphurieng/datafiles/images/img/8.jpg\" width=\"1200\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the criterion: &quot;Overcoming yourself, integration, prestige, all for the development&quot;, VRG always wishes to expand relationships with all partners in the spirit of cooperation, mutual benefit, mutual development. development.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2. Scope of activities:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Buying and selling, exporting all kinds of natural rubber.</li>\r\n	<li>Buy raw materials to process natural rubber products.</li>\r\n	<li>Supply natural rubber to manufacturers.</li>\r\n	<li>Import natural rubber, skim block and artificial rubber.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>3. Business Capacity:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Rubber: Capable of supplying up to 1000 tons / shipment</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>4. Partners - Customers:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Domestic rubber processing manufacturers are state-controlled.</li>\r\n	<li>Private rubber manufacturers and processors.</li>\r\n	<li>Merchants in rubber processing materials.</li>\r\n	<li>Domestic rubber trading units.</li>\r\n	<li>Foreign partners include traders, brokers and production units</li>\r\n</ul>'', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, ''doan-thanh-nien-cao-su-phu-rieng-chung-tay-day-lui-dich-benh-covid-19-cp-202521589719027'', NULL, 19, ''1589719045_16.jpg'', NULL, NULL, ''datafiles'', 1589689077, 0, 1, 9, 0, 0, ''Đoàn Thanh niên Cao su Phú Riềng chung tay đẩy lùi dịch bệnh COVID-19'', ''The Phu Rieng Rubber Youth Union joins hands to fight off the COVID-19 disease'', NULL, ''Đoàn Thanh niên Cao su Phú Riềng chung tay đẩy lùi dịch bệnh COVID-19'', ''The Phu Rieng Rubber Youth Union joins hands to fight off the COVID-19 disease'', NULL, ''Đoàn Thanh niên Cao su Phú Riềng chung tay đẩy lùi dịch bệnh COVID-19'', ''The Phu Rieng Rubber Youth Union joins hands to fight off the COVID-19 disease'', NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
