ors.</li>\r\n	<li>Merchants in rubber processing materials.</li>\r\n	<li>Domestic rubber trading units.</li>\r\n	<li>Foreign partners include traders, brokers and production units</li>\r\n</ul>'', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, ''doan-thanh-nien-cao-su-phu-rieng-chung-tay-day-lui-dich-benh-covid-19-cp-566891589719105'', NULL, 8, ''1589719116_19.jpg'', NULL, NULL, ''datafiles'', 1589689077, 0, 1, 12, 0, 0, ''Đoàn Thanh niên Cao su Phú Riềng chung tay đẩy lùi dịch bệnh COVID-19'', ''The Phu Rieng Rubber Youth Union joins hands to fight off the COVID-19 disease'', NULL, ''Đoàn Thanh niên Cao su Phú Riềng chung tay đẩy lùi dịch bệnh COVID-19'', ''The Phu Rieng Rubber Youth Union joins hands to fight off the COVID-19 disease'', NULL, ''Đoàn Thanh niên Cao su Phú Riềng chung tay đẩy lùi dịch bệnh COVID-19'', ''The Phu Rieng Rubber Youth Union joins hands to fight off the COVID-19 disease'', NULL, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
